org.workflowsim

Class WorkflowPlanner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core.SimEntity
      • org.workflowsim.WorkflowPlanner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class WorkflowPlanner
extends SimEntity
    WorkflowPlanner supports dynamic planning. In the future we will have global and static algorithm here. The WorkflowSim starts from WorkflowPlanner.
    Since:
    WorkflowSim Toolkit 1.0
